UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`=' I\'m impressed, $N. I would\'ve thought that the Grimtotem criminals would\'ve been more difficult to locate. The Alliance are truly incompetent. In truth, I just sought to answer the death of one of my men, but this situation has been more fortunate than expected. If the Grimtotem choose to retaliate, it will likely be against the Alliance. Perhaps we will soon have the manpower to drive the scum from these shores once and for all.' WHERE `word_id` = 184012; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27297
