UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Escort Thrall safely to Wyrmrest' WHERE `word_id` = 191531; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=30103
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Ethereals?  Goods delivered to Tuurem?  Exotic engineering parts?  And a blood elf getting ready to deliver this last box to Firewing Point?$B$BWhat does all of this mean?!  How does it relate to what happened to the druids in the Cenarion Thicket?$B$BI think we should have a look inside that box.' WHERE `word_id` = 149203; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9990
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Eureka! My genius saves the day yet again! Take that Bamm Megabomb! And now, to reap the benefits!' WHERE `word_id` = 175418; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24744
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even for a creature of that size, this heart is far too large. It struggled to keep up with the creature\'s gigantic body. I have little doubt it would\'ve died before reaching half its normal lifespan.$B$BEven with such risks, I\'m determined to convince the Consortium to share their technology. There\'s too much promise here to give up now.' WHERE `word_id` = 151014; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10429
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even if the flowers died out shortly after they bloomed, they proved our point to the Scourge: they are losing, and we are winning. Thank you for your assistance.' WHERE `word_id` = 184404; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27421
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even in dreams I did not dare foresee this day.$B$BBehold, mortal.$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO IS OLDER THAN EXISTENCE!$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO HAS FACED TITAN AND GOD ALIKE!$B$BRISE MY MASTER! BREAK FROM YOUR BONDS!' WHERE `word_id` = 142472; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=7786
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even now I can feel the pulse of nature from within these seeds.$B$BWe must put them to good use!' WHERE `word_id` = 159761; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12458
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even now, only the S.A.F.E. teams dare to venture far into the city to search for survivors. Meanwhile, Thermaplugg has sent one of his followers, Crushcog, to distract us and buy time for him to dig in.' WHERE `word_id` = 180264; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26208
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even the chieftain is beginning to lose his memories? The past is being rewritten before our eyes and if we do not find out who is behind this, the entire legacy of Stormhoof could be lost forever.' WHERE `word_id` = 162276; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13037
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Even the mighty wyrms had to heed his call. How is a simple mortal like you going to resist him?' WHERE `word_id` = 163656; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13359
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Ever does the time grow nearer when we shall launch ourselves headlong into the conflagration at Ahn\'Qiraj, priest. But first we must gather our strength and prepare so that we can survive the onslaught of the insects and their masters.$B$BIf you are here again, then surely you wish to make another contribution of runecloth bandages to the war effort? Please do so as soon as you can and return to me once more.' WHERE `word_id` = 144025; -- locales_quest - details : entry=8610
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Eversong Ranger Blessed' WHERE `word_id` = 147199; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=9489
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Every day is a gift. Make the most of it. For tomorrow we shall stride swifter over the plains than today. We will spread our arms further and strain to achieve that which tonight we can only dream of, though it may ever elude us.' WHERE `word_id` = 148680; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9854
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Every soldier we deny to the Scourge is more than one life saved.$B$BThank you.' WHERE `word_id` = 191475; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29864
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everyone in Dolanaar is so proud of Sister Aquinne. I\'m certain she\'ll be pleased to receive this thoughtful gift from Nyoma.$B$BWhen you\'re ready to travel to Darnassus, just speak to me again and for a few coins, you can hire a hippogryph to take you there. I\'m told Sister Aquinne enjoys the solitude of a small plaza just south of the hippogryph master in Darnassus. Look for her there after you arrive.' WHERE `word_id` = 168006; -- locales_quest - details : entry=6341
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everyone is proud. Proud that our people will live to see another winter. But beyond that? What is there?$B$BMaybe you should lead this clan, $N. Maybe then I will be allowed to die when the Greatmother passes. Allowed to finally erase the shame of my family name. I long for such peace.' WHERE `word_id` = 149926; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10171
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everyone will be so pleased: Chef Jessen\'s Soothing Turtle Bisque is served once again!' WHERE `word_id` = 132519; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=555
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everything here seems to be in working order.' WHERE `word_id` = 177878; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25564
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everything was fine until the Scourge attacked. They took off with Dargath, Gerk and Burr and they also destroyed our ride. Guess who led that attack?$B$B<MacKellar nods.>$B$BNavarius...$B$BSeems this whole area is some type of factory for Scourge. We\'re in the middle of a damned undead mine field!' WHERE `word_id` = 161697; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12894
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everywhere we have fought the Scourge, we have taught them to fear us and this campaign will be no different.' WHERE `word_id` = 164446; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13864
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Everywhere we have met the Scourge, we have made them fear us, and this campaign is no different.' WHERE `word_id` = 164445; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13863
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Ew, that\'s a stink if I ever smelled one!$B$BGo on now, put it down right here. I\'ll cast my spell and she\'ll be swabbin\' soap for sure!' WHERE `word_id` = 156681; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11469
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Exactly what I needed. You\'ll be an asset to the Forsaken, $N. You know, word has it that you were quite the $C in your previous life. Perhaps I should assign you to a more exciting task.' WHERE `word_id` = 188760; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28608
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examine Halazzi\'s chamber' WHERE `word_id` = 153914; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=11166
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examine Jan\'alai\'s platform' WHERE `word_id` = 153915; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText2 : entry=11166
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examined the Alliance Plans' WHERE `word_id` = 178372; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=25695
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examined the Horde Plans' WHERE `word_id` = 180144; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=26174
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examining the book carefully, you conclude that it must be a journal. Its pages are filled with an elegant script differing from that of the map. The text of many of the pages is obscured by drawings and writing in the mapmaker\'s hand.$B$BIt\'s nearly impossible to make out the text beneath the mapmaker\'s tales of drunken carousing during shore leave.' WHERE `word_id` = 147445; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9550
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examining the gazebo reveals some interesting and unusual things in contrast to the surrounding ruins.$B$BFirst, the gazebo is clearly a more recent construction than the other objects in the ruins. Second, the gazebo has a small series of glyphs engraved into the sides of it; the glyphs repeat in their pattern, but it otherwise is unknown in origin and meaning. Third, the stone of the gazebo itself is warm to the touch.$B$BThis certainly quantifies as "standing out" in the search of the ruins!' WHERE `word_id` = 137327; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=2866
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Examining the map reveals it to be the battle plans that Hadoken Swiftstrider wants. Numerous arrows that perhaps represent troop movements are drawn on the map, though most seem to be headed toward the south rather than to the north where Camp Mojache lies.$B$BAnother section of the map has a picture of what you think is a large insect of some kind, with various tick marks under it. From the looks of the gnolls, it perhaps represents their losses against the unknown bugs...' WHERE `word_id` = 275785; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25365
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Exarch Menelaous Warned' WHERE `word_id` = 147859; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText2 : entry=9663
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent - please enjoy these dumplings with my compliments. While they are but a small token of appreciation for the honor you have brought upon yourself through your actions, I think you will enjoy them all the same.$B$BShould you have any more coins of ancestry, I stand ready to offer you a wide array of items in exchange.' WHERE `word_id` = 144449; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8863
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent - the more water pouches we are able to reclaim, the further away from disaster we\'ll all be! Keep \'em coming, and I will be sure to reward you for every five water pouches you bring me.' WHERE `word_id` = 136181; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1707
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent - this morrowgrain will no doubt help when the time comes. We know that the night elves are conducting similar research into these herbs, though it isn\'t clear to what end they will use them for if they discover anything. The Arch Druid thinks that the need for morrowgrain will remain until we\'ve figured out the mysteries behind this herb.$B$BThis is for you, $N. The Cenarion Circle thanks you for your continued support.' WHERE `word_id` = 138493; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3804
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent - this morrowgrain will no doubt please the Arch Druid. I must admit though... just being near them makes me feel a little uncomfortable. I can only imagine how difficult it is for the Arch Druid to tolerate them in such large numbers!$B$BThis is for you, $N. The Cenarion Circle thanks you for your continued support.' WHERE `word_id` = 138490; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3803
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE `word_id` = 143023; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8195
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent and precise work, $N. Your diligence is to be commended, as is your celerity. I will personally see to it that none of these purple lotus go to waste.$B$BThank you again, and should you come by more purple lotus do not hesitate to bring them to me with utmost haste.' WHERE `word_id` = 143936; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8583
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent and timely! Well done, $Glad:lass;.' WHERE `word_id` = 144436; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8859
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N!  Selenn\'s help in holding back the vortex will be invaluable.' WHERE `word_id` = 172252; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13585
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N!  You\'ve outdone yourself this time.' WHERE `word_id` = 177056; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25308
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N! Let us see what can be learned from these briefings.' WHERE `word_id` = 150642; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10328
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N! That\'ll show those bird men the meaning of air superiority!' WHERE `word_id` = 153288; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11008
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N! With your help the Strand of the Ancients will be under complete Alliance control.' WHERE `word_id` = 163788; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13405
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Don\'t worry, they\'re not stuck in that form permanently. Their apprenticeship, however, won\'t be restored until they earn it back.' WHERE `word_id` = 146232; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9066
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Now give me a moment to examine the plans you\'ve brought me.' WHERE `word_id` = 172291; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13596
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Or should I say: "$N"damus? Give me a minute to read these.' WHERE `word_id` = 177012; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25296
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Our troops will hear of your deeds.' WHERE `word_id` = 188293; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28483
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. We\'re one step closer to saving Azeroth!' WHERE `word_id` = 163941; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13606
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. With Battok dead, I\'ll send the signal to Captain Tharran. This should be the end of the Frostmane threat.' WHERE `word_id` = 178910; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25840
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. With the legionnaires broken, it will be easier to face the Fel Horde on the battlefield, though they remain a formidable enemy.' WHERE `word_id` = 147231; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9496
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. With your dedication we\'re sure to defeat our enemy.' WHERE `word_id` = 150263; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10246
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Without your help those prisoners would\'ve lost their minds and souls to the Scourge.' WHERE `word_id` = 146384; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9164
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. You might not think this adds up to much, but this might very well be the difference between life and death to one of our soldiers.' WHERE `word_id` = 187310; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28200
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent job, user $N. We must obtain access to the fusion core now.' WHERE `word_id` = 185736; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27777
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE `word_id` = 164950; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11335
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent news, $N. With the locals\' help we\'ll have the logistical support we need to outmaneuver the Horde in this region.$B$BI have further tasks for you if you\'re interested.' WHERE `word_id` = 159411; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12294
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent recovery, $N! I never thought I\'d see these tools again.' WHERE `word_id` = 130660; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=125
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent targeting, $G sir : ma\'am;! I\'ll have to remember to buy a round for the cannoneers back at the keep.' WHERE `word_id` = 155275; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11245
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work $N - every bit of this, once we purify it, will help us take back Felwood. Here, take some doses of Cenarion plant salve and head into the forest. The reclaiming of the land from the corruption waits for no $R!' WHERE `word_id` = 138750; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4105
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work my friend. I think you\'ll go far within the Horde.' WHERE `word_id` = 133829; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=875
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work!  I\'ll put a good word in for you.' WHERE `word_id` = 143301; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8319
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work!  It might not be quite as daring as plundering the high seas, but I\'d be a darned son of a deckswabber if I passed on this opportunity.' WHERE `word_id` = 156626; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11455
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work!  Now if only I can convince Jerrod to let us move our operation into that shack...' WHERE `word_id` = 175949; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24998
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! Digging around for that copper and smelting it must have been quite an adventure. Unless you bought them at the auction house. Either way, it works for me. You are to be commended for your contribution to the war effort, $C. And please don\'t hesitate to bring me more copper bars if you have them.' WHERE `word_id` = 143629; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8493
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! I am currently researching the Warmaul tribe that the Boulderfist lieutenant mentioned. Now the tasks you have performed must be tested.' WHERE `word_id` = 148953; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9922
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! Let me see those documents. Hmm. Now we know exactly when and where the final negotiations will happen. Don\'t worry if those robes don\'t fit you - I\'ve got it all worked out.' WHERE `word_id` = 174364; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14433
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! Oh, it won\'t stop the iron dwarves, but it\'ll take them valuable time to rebuild those forges. I daresay we\'ve gained the advantage.' WHERE `word_id` = 162113; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12988
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! The most difficult part of the project is done. Now, all we need is a way to get these back to Area 52 and attract the interest of the Cenarion Expedition as well. There should be enough here for our own needs and to earn a little profit on the side.' WHERE `word_id` = 151042; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10435
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! The time has come to test the new formula. If this works, not only should that captured leper gnome be cured, but I should have a full head of hair! Stand back!' WHERE `word_id` = 137426; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=2926
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work! These look just like the others. Thank you for your help.$B$BIf you ever want to help again, look for me next time the Darkmoon Faire is in town.' WHERE `word_id` = 191064; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29517
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $C. I will get some of our own patrols out to make sure that no more naga get within sight of this cave. We should have the area secured within the hour.' WHERE `word_id` = 177912; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25579
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $C. Kael\'s armies will falter and once we take the harbor we shall deliver the killing blow!' WHERE `word_id` = 154532; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11539
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $C. May the Light continue to protect you.' WHERE `word_id` = 152465; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10816
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $C.$B$BI will get some patrols out of our own to make sure that no more naga get within sight of this cave. We should have the area secured within the hour.' WHERE `word_id` = 179403; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25952
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $Gsir:ma\'am;!$B$BI\'ll see to it that the commander is apprised of your mission results.' WHERE `word_id` = 160240; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12562
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N! Eliminating Vyletongue\'s presence is a key step to freeing me and, ultimately, saving these lands from corruption. Take this as a token of my thanks and an incentive to continue your work here.' WHERE `word_id` = 185434; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27697
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N! These transmutations are perfect in every way!$B$BI will now teach you the manner in which the alchemical transmutation process can conjure matter out of thin air! Make good use of your knowledge, master transmuter.$B$BNow, if you\'ll excuse me, I have to go see a buyer interested in primal might.' WHERE `word_id` = 152830; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10899
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N! We now have a point from which we can plan our counter-attack.' WHERE `word_id` = 149207; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9991
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N! You took out a good chunk of their dragon riders and really pissed off their leadership.$B$BAre you ready to head back to Valgarde and report the good news to Zorek? If so, I\'ve got a crazy idea!' WHERE `word_id` = 156545; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11421
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N! Your victory over Varedis will have a tremendous impact on our war against Illidan.$B$BYou\'ve proven yourself not just to the Aldor but to all of Outland. Allow me to destroy what remains of that horrible book.' WHERE `word_id` = 151863; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10651
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Are you certain you haven\'t done this before?' WHERE `word_id` = 184334; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27389
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. At the very least, you have bought us more time - precious, precious time.' WHERE `word_id` = 139791; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5081
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. I didn\'t think those gnolls would give you much trouble.' WHERE `word_id` = 177426; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25426
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. I think I speak for everyone when I say the sooner we get out of here, the better.' WHERE `word_id` = 174431; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14463
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. I\'ll see that these are, ah, disposed of immediately.$B$BAfter all, what would our fine apothecaries want with an army of monstrous, poison-spitting, flesh-eating super-toads?' WHERE `word_id` = 190216; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29319
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. It will take the Riverpaw weeks to recover from the blow you just dealt. Please take an item of your choosing as a reward for what you have done.' WHERE `word_id` = 180550; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26288
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Now comes the fun part.' WHERE `word_id` = 175875; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24976
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Now for one last bit of information.' WHERE `word_id` = 157915; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11942
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Now we\'re a bit safer from dinosaur attacks... plus I\'ve got all this fresh meat to serve to my men.' WHERE `word_id` = 175287; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24697
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Our plan\'s almost come together.' WHERE `word_id` = 177079; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25314
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Possession of the phylactery will be the key to our victory. When you enter battle with Naberius, I will smash it, exposing him to your attacks.' WHERE `word_id` = 150602; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10319
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The demons might repair the gateway in due time. I suppose we\'ll just have to blow it up again.' WHERE `word_id` = 154459; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11516
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The eternal battle wages on, but we\'ve tipped the scales in favor of the pirates today. Firallon will be happy to hear the news.' WHERE `word_id` = 181842; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26648
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The gnome technology, while somewhat obnoxious, is highly effective. We should now have a clear path to Windshear Hold.' WHERE `word_id` = 178039; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25614
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE `word_id` = 155989; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11338
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The naga will learn not to underestimate us.' WHERE `word_id` = 148277; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9766
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The note you captured makes sense in light of this ritual the infiltrators mentioned. This city is infested with cultists and their sympathizers. We must act before their plans can come to fruition.' WHERE `word_id` = 171959; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27749
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The Scryers have uncovered valuable information thanks to your distraction. Maybe they\'ll actually share it with us this time.' WHERE `word_id` = 150242; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10241
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The tremors have already begun to subside.$B$BWith any luck, your efforts have granted us sufficient time to find a way to thwart Malygos\' efforts.' WHERE `word_id` = 157801; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11905
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. There is certainly a latent power here, one that not even constant exposure to the corruption of the satyr can dim. Do you see how it still shines, after all these years?' WHERE `word_id` = 147311; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26455
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. These $R will regret ever setting foot in our lands.' WHERE `word_id` = 173785; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14276
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Twilight\'s Hammer will think twice before trying to turn our own people against us again. I\'m sure I\'m not the only one troubled by just how many citizens were taken in by their message. Times aren\'t exactly easy, but if you have no honor or loyalty, you have nothing.' WHERE `word_id` = 171839; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25348
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Twilight\'s Hammer will think twice before trying to turn our own people against us again.$B$BWhat worries me is how many citizens joined their movement without thinking about the cult\'s empty promises. Are times so dire that people will abandon the Light for promises of power and immortality?' WHERE `word_id` = 171872; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25418
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. We are closing in on Nesingwary!' WHERE `word_id` = 157673; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11872
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. We might win this one yet.' WHERE `word_id` = 178018; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25608
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. We shall soon claim victory in Hyjal. It has been an honor to fight along your side.' WHERE `word_id` = 177830; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25550
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. When our forces from Vengeance Landing arrive, we\'ll be able to take care of any vrykul that are left.' WHERE `word_id` = 159873; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12482
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 145994; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8463
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. With the shadows destroyed, it can only be a matter of time before the Lich King decides to recall his necropolises and leave us in peace.' WHERE `word_id` = 145401; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9368
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. With the shadows destroyed, our hope of victory against the Lich King survives.' WHERE `word_id` = 272250; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9085
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. With their leader removed, our efforts against these vrykul should be more successful.$B$BService such as this cannot go unrewarded!' WHERE `word_id` = 156086; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11262
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Without their tunnelers, the silithid will have a hard time repairing any damage inflicted to their hive\'s structure. I assume you\'ll want a new task.' WHERE `word_id` = 272083; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8687
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Without their workers, the silithid will have a hard time repairing any damage inflicted to their hive\'s structure.' WHERE `word_id` = 143668; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8502
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Without you, Valiance Keep might\'ve not held against the attackers. Thanks to your help we\'ll live to fight another day.' WHERE `word_id` = 157755; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11897
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. You are incredibly resilient to this blight. We\'ll have to take you in for testing some time.' WHERE `word_id` = 187814; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28325
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. You\'re a worthy ally.' WHERE `word_id` = 143819; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8539
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. You\'ve turned out to be quite an asset to this garrison. It\'s time for you to train!' WHERE `word_id` = 189227; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28759
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. You\'ve turned out to be quite an asset to this garrison.$B$BFeel free to speak with any of our trainers within and around the abbey if you need to sharpen any of your combat skills.$B$BWhen you\'re ready, I have another assignment for you...' WHERE `word_id` = 189551; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29079
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Your diligence is as noteworthy as always.' WHERE `word_id` = 144280; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8770
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Your part in the attack on Hive\'Ashi has been noted.' WHERE `word_id` = 143663; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8501
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Your part in the attack on Hive\'Regal has been noted.' WHERE `word_id` = 144295; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8774
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Your part in the attack on Hive\'Zora has been noted.' WHERE `word_id` = 144287; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8772
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Your reputation is well-deserved.' WHERE `word_id` = 189252; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28781
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N.$B$BI am sure that this is a piece of shadoweave that you have not yet seen.' WHERE `word_id` = 138054; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3379
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N.$B$BI thank you for your assistance.' WHERE `word_id` = 160435; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12610
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N.$B$BThank you again for your help!' WHERE `word_id` = 154474; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11521
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N.$B$BWe\'ll have him prepared for his interrogation at once.' WHERE `word_id` = 156923; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11590
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $N... although I\'m afraid I haven\'t been nearly as productive as you have.' WHERE `word_id` = 179210; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25907
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $R. Alexi deserves nothing for his foolishness.' WHERE `word_id` = 183620; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27143
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $R. Now to secure my inheritance...' WHERE `word_id` = 140276; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5341
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, $R. Should you find any more tomes, do not hesitate to return them to us.$B$BAs time passes, we tend to change around and even add new rewards for the return of missing tomes.' WHERE `word_id` = 142132; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=7498
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, captain! Lord Illidan will hear of your heroism!' WHERE `word_id` = 153620; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11086
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, Earthenfurydamus. I\'m having the servants you chose for me briefed on their new duties.' WHERE `word_id` = 177135; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25330
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, Earthenfurydamus. We must show all would-be competitors that we are not ones to give up easily.' WHERE `word_id` = 177064; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25310
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, friend. I like the way you do business.' WHERE `word_id` = 178293; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25678
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, imbecile. I shall fashion this fur into something you can use.' WHERE `word_id` = 141062; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=6135
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, mon! I do hope they had a good time!' WHERE `word_id` = 148500; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9816
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, my boy! The Town-In-A-Box is saved and the Bilgewater Cartel will be profitable once again thanks to my overwhelmingly unbelievable intellect and tinkering know-how.' WHERE `word_id` = 175500; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24817
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, overseer. Mor\'ghor will hear of your outstanding service to the Dragonmaw.$B$BNow back to these Murkblood dogs. They plan an escape, eh? Dare they defy the one true lord of Outland? Their masters will pay for this!' WHERE `word_id` = 153597; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11081
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, soldier. We could use more able bodies like you around here - stop by another day if the operation hasn\'t wrapped up.' WHERE `word_id` = 163468; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13309
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work, young one.' WHERE `word_id` = 162439; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13074
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. Hopefully the raids will stop for now. I have one more task for you, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 180518; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26280
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. I can now continue my work without the distractions of that great white beast. I shall fashion this fur into something you can use.' WHERE `word_id` = 184817; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27523
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. I will send for our reinforcements right away.' WHERE `word_id` = 190412; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29199
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. I\'ll keep a close eye on the ones you tagged and see if they mature as quickly as the other lifeforms in the dome.$B$BWith the proper control, we could use this technology to regrow the ruined areas of Outland and Azeroth.' WHERE `word_id` = 151004; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10427
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. It seems more death knights remained loyal to Arthas than I initially thought.$B$BHe certainly is sparing nothing in his attempt to replace Acherus. A pure Saronite citadel would be hard to destroy indeed. There\'s no need to destroy it though... we can halt production and put down these death knight leaders here and now, before they become a real threat.$B$BMost importantly, we need to disrupt them enough to get those death knights away from from the leaders so that we can make our strike.' WHERE `word_id` = 162777; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13145
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. Keep your fingers crossed, $N. I\'m going to activate the shield.' WHERE `word_id` = 150234; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10240
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. No one could tell me who this leader might be, but I was able to uncover the name of someone who will have our answer.' WHERE `word_id` = 158739; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12149
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Caladis Brightspear as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the book falling back into Sunreaver hands.$B$BI\'ll ensure that Shandy Glossgleam gets his tabard back without incident, along with a healthy reward for his help.' WHERE `word_id` = 164949; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=20439
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Myralion Sunblaze as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the Silver Covenant taking the book from us again.$B$BI\'ll get that tabard back to Shandy and see that he\'s well compensated for his assistance. Once the book is in Myralion\'s hands, the Silver Covenant won\'t be a threat anymore.' WHERE `word_id` = 164966; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24451
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. One more threat we can worry a bit less about. We\'ll continue the offensive while they are still off-guard.' WHERE `word_id` = 172010; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13507
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. Only two manaforges remain active.$B$BSoon Kael\'thas will be cut off from his main source of power.' WHERE `word_id` = 150612; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10321
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. That should slow them down a bit.' WHERE `word_id` = 172018; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13509
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. We should have little threat in the air then.' WHERE `word_id` = 162909; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13171
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent work. We were in short supply of these, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 144338; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8786
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  All who oppose us will be crushed!' WHERE `word_id` = 150948; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10415
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  I can\'t wait to read these. Please do keep bringing the encrypted texts here if you find them.' WHERE `word_id` = 143321; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8324
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  I will get to decoding these as soon as possible. If I find anything of interest I\'ll find some way to get the information to you.' WHERE `word_id` = 143318; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8323
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  I\'ll make sure these get taken to a safe place.' WHERE `word_id` = 173277; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14094
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  I\'ll stash these away, maybe they\'ll be useful later.' WHERE `word_id` = 143298; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8318
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  I\'m almost done here.' WHERE `word_id` = 174298; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14412
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  Let us begin.$B$BThe first skill you will learn is that of the Primal Strike. The primal spirits, when called upon, will strengthen your arm to deliver a mighty blow.$B$BHelpful, isn\'t it?' WHERE `word_id` = 174875; -- locales_quest - details : entry=24527
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  Let\'s get started.$B$BFirst, you\'re going to have to learn the spell Arcane Missiles. This spell is a little bit different from others you\'ve learned in the past. Each time you cast another spell, you have a chance to create an opening to use Arcane Missiles. Why not get a feel for the spell using those training dummies the militia trainees put up outside the entrance to Anvilmar?' WHERE `word_id` = 174871; -- locales_quest - details : entry=24526
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  Our pup is ready for a fight.' WHERE `word_id` = 177626; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25494
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  Such a personal item carries a strong scent of the intruders--enough to guide Whisper into their ranks...' WHERE `word_id` = 147094; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9460
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  Take this. I\'ve prepared this bundle with the items you obtained. They will allow you to summon Terokk.$B$BBeware, $N. He is the most powerful arakkoa to ever exist. Do not underestimate him!' WHERE `word_id` = 153562; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11072
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  That little backstabber won\'t be running off with anyone\'s husband any time soon.$B$BHere\'s a little something for your troubles. I trust we can keep this incident between us, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 147144; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9472
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  That should be the last thing I need to test out the new bombs. Just a moment and I\'ll try this out!' WHERE `word_id` = 158293; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12047
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  The information I need should be in here.' WHERE `word_id` = 157817; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11908
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  These spines will be invaluable to my research!  When I find a cure for the plague and word of my name spreads I\'ll make sure to make mention of you!$B$BIn the meantime, take these as a reward. You might need them if you decide to go back to the coast.' WHERE `word_id` = 146322; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9149
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  They\'re even sharper than I expected them to be. I\'ll pack them in the snow until the bomb is ready.$B$BLet\'s see... what next...' WHERE `word_id` = 158283; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12045
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  We were in need of these, $N. Thanks.' WHERE `word_id` = 272034; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8497
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  We\'ll bury these immediately. Those Explorers\' League dimwits will never suspect us!' WHERE `word_id` = 186105; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27877
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  You\'ve managed to complete the simplest of tasks without dying. Now that that\'s out of the way...' WHERE `word_id` = 180105; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26158
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!  You\'ve proven to be a valuable ally in preparing for the war against the silithid.' WHERE `word_id` = 143181; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8281
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! A fair tradeoff, if I do say so myself. Watch and learn, $N!' WHERE `word_id` = 137176; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=2771
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Even these fools will soon know that to stand against the Horde means death.' WHERE `word_id` = 176886; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25252
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I am a Tauren of my word, $R. The arrows are yours.' WHERE `word_id` = 141985; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=7341
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I can go back to my... leisurely... hunting now. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 130915; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=183
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I can\'t wait to present this project to my superiors!' WHERE `word_id` = 191337; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29686
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I should have this here engine samophlanginated within the hour.' WHERE `word_id` = 180831; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26361
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I suspect that without Jammal\'an\'s leadership, the trolls will fall to infighting and Hakkar will never set his eyes upon our world.' WHERE `word_id` = 185077; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27604
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I think the holy water will prove devastating in large volumes.' WHERE `word_id` = 184194; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27352
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I wish I could\'ve seen the look on that Rear Admiral\'s face when his flagship went up like a candle. Let me use my telescope here to take a look at the damage. What - Whhhaaatt!? That thing is still floating? Hartley must\'ve moved the munitions ashore in case his ship was mined. I underestimated you, Hartley... but for the last time!' WHERE `word_id` = 173161; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14038
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! I\'ll get the crew to work right away on the parts we\'ll need for the next race.' WHERE `word_id` = 135100; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1192
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! It is no small sacrifice that you\'ve made to earn these signets, and you will be acknowledged for your service appropriately. It\'s adventurers like you, $N, that truly make a difference.$B$BLet me know if you have additional signets to hand in; I\'ll gladly help you out with whatever ones you need exchanged.' WHERE `word_id` = 144392; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8819
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! It is only a matter of time before the son of Deathwing feels my claws.' WHERE `word_id` = 184474; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27445
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! It looks like you\'re eager to learn, so let\'s get to it. I will teach you how to make the most out of the plants you use in your alchemical potions.$B$BYou will find that you can make herbs go a really long way if you know what you\'re doing. Sometimes you will be able to make two potion with materials you initially judged necessary for just one.' WHERE `word_id` = 152820; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10897
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! It seems we\'ve appointed dutiful Flamekeepers this year if the bonfires are as well-kept as you claim. Thank you for inspecting them for me; here, take this as a small token of my esteem.' WHERE `word_id` = 145398; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9367
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! It was crucial that we collect that intelligence.$B$BWell done, friend.' WHERE `word_id` = 157209; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11648
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Just as I was running low!$B$BYou say Deliana sent you?' WHERE `word_id` = 144561; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8922
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Just as I was running low!$B$BYou say Mokvar sent you?' WHERE `word_id` = 144564; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8923
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Let me make a few adjustments here and we should be good to go.' WHERE `word_id` = 181318; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26510
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Let the naga retreat back into the seas where they belong!' WHERE `word_id` = 172761; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13901
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Let\'s hope the damage wasn\'t permanent. Judging by the poor victims still in camp here, the Twilight\'s Hammer really messed with their heads.' WHERE `word_id` = 177020; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25298
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Let\'s perform the trade then. It\'s hard to part with this excellent armor, but I\'m afraid I won\'t be needing it any time soon.$B$BIf you\'re interested in performing more work for me, I might be willing to give up the rest of the pieces.' WHERE `word_id` = 144529; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10492
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Most excellent, $C!$B$BWhat you have done this day is only the first step in a much broader foundation--a foundation that we will build the destruction of the Shadow Council on, once and for all.$B$BTell me all he said... and leave not one word out--it may be more important than you realize.' WHERE `word_id` = 140660; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5727
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Now just a few adjustments and this thing will be as good as new. Oh yes, your key! Here you go.$B$BBy the way, the Jump-a-tron still has a few kinks that I need to work out. Um, just be careful.' WHERE `word_id` = 335239; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10109
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Now to calibrate the device.' WHERE `word_id` = 150902; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10405
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Now to prepare the "meal."' WHERE `word_id` = 183416; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27082
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Our next target will be the Laughing Skull Ruins.' WHERE `word_id` = 148981; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9928
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Take this. I\'ve prepared this bundle with items symbolizing the foes you\'ve defeated. They will allow you to summon Terokk.$B$BBeware, $N. He is the most powerful arakkoa to ever exist. Do not underestimate him!' WHERE `word_id` = 154689; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11885
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Thanks to you, I should be able to complete the order in time. To show my gratitude, I would like to offer some coin as compensation for your troubles.$B$BThank you and farewell.' WHERE `word_id` = 140492; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5545
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! That should put a dent in their war machines!' WHERE `word_id` = 163019; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13200
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! That\'ll show Kael\'thas not to underestimate our power.' WHERE `word_id` = 151885; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10658
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! These materials, combined with the muisek, should yield just the results we\'ve been wanting.' WHERE `word_id` = 137917; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3128
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! These will do nicely. Here\'s a reward for your hard work.' WHERE `word_id` = 182687; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26890
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This book catalogs the descendants of Terokk\'s ancient enemies. It is prophesied that their demise will be followed by Terokk\'s return.' WHERE `word_id` = 153375; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11029
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This Tiara will grant me complete control of the water around here, and the Electrified Scale will serve to power all the machines I need to use it all to my advantage! You\'re going to make me a very rich and powerful goblin! You can have this, it\'s nothing compared to what I\'ll have soon.' WHERE `word_id` = 183374; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27070
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This will be invaluable in my continued studies of the machinations of the Scourge. Thank you, $N, and if you find more of these scales please bring them to me!' WHERE `word_id` = 140508; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5582
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This will help fuel the flames of war for days to come.' WHERE `word_id` = 155495; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13154
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This will help me keep our soldiers in weapons and armor.$B$BYour help is truly making a difference!' WHERE `word_id` = 154517; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11536
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This will help protect our troops against the cold.' WHERE `word_id` = 162834; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13156
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! This will help us defeat the Alliance in the battles to come!' WHERE `word_id` = 162993; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13191
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Though small in size, this fragment is teeming with energy, I can feel it!' WHERE `word_id` = 147918; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9680
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! We\'re getting closer....$B$BSoon I\'ll be able to craft an anvil, then the real work can begin.' WHERE `word_id` = 154513; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11535
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! When I\'m through with you, you will be able to slip among the Sunfury ranks unnoticed.' WHERE `word_id` = 150037; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10197
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! With all of this power that you\'ve recovered we\'ll be able to keep the machinery running for a little while, anyway.$B$BThe Zephyrium Capacitorium is a real pig when it comes to power consumption!$B$BI hope dealing with those electromentals wasn\'t too difficult. I have something else in mind for you to do, and I have a feeling that it\'s going to be a little more dangerous.' WHERE `word_id` = 151591; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10584
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! With Deathclasp gone we\'re free to use the southern mountain range as a strategic path to circumvent the silithid hives. Your work is greatly appreciated.' WHERE `word_id` = 143191; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8283
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! With these guts and the ferocious doomweed we\'ll be able to test out our new strain of blight. Now to select a suitable target...' WHERE `word_id` = 183075; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26995
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! With this roster we can make more educated decisions when targeting Kael\'s followers at the manaforges.$B$BIt\'s too bad, I was beginning to take a liking to killing his lackeys indiscriminately.' WHERE `word_id` = 150001; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10189
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! Yes, yes, these will do just fine!' WHERE `word_id` = 156300; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11309
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! You are an apt pupil, $N.$B$BNow comes the fun part. Deployment!' WHERE `word_id` = 156286; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11306
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! You\'re a life saver. These dumplings turned out to be quite good. Didn\'t really expect such good taste from the Twilight\'s Hammer.' WHERE `word_id` = 143293; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8317
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! You\'re my kind of $C, $N.$B$BWith your help, we will throw these invaders back into the sea.' WHERE `word_id` = 175070; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24618
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent! You\'ve done well, $N. I\'m not sure I trust the goblin\'s craftsmanship, but I\'m left with no other choice.' WHERE `word_id` = 144706; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8977
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!$B$B$N, you\'ve helped bolster our forces here, and you\'ve saved many of these forest creatures from the Horde as well. With our army now ready, Feathermoon will stand against all threats, Horde or otherwise!$B$BOn behalf of Lady Feathermoon, I\'d like to award you with this weapon, fit for a Sentinel.' WHERE `word_id` = 177556; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25469
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!$B$B<A fierce grin creeps onto Ricket\'s face.>$B$BLet the destruction begin!' WHERE `word_id` = 161359; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12821
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!$B$BLet\'s see what this is about...' WHERE `word_id` = 132956; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=658
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!$B$BThe forsaken will resort to any means necessary to crush the alliance! The use of the corrupted water will surely prove useful in our future efforts...' WHERE `word_id` = 139201; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4506
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!$B$BThe totem I will craft for you is more than a symbol of your status among $C--it has abilities beyond that. One use of the totem is as a focus for spells. Those spells are tied to the earth, and as you earn greater and greater wisdom, more of the earth\'s abilities will be made accessible to you.$B$BThe trainers will know when you are ready for greater knowledge.$B$BBut for now, take this earth totem, and a scroll to teach you your first ability.' WHERE `word_id` = 135884; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1518
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent!$B$BYour undercover work has truly paid off, $N.$B$BNow let\'s have a look at that scepter....' WHERE `word_id` = 160753; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12676
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $C! A job well done. I\'ll see to it that those bars get onto the pallet and into the hands of the blacksmiths and engineers that are hard at work building up the supplies for our army. Thank you again, and if you come across more thorium bars be sure to drop by.' WHERE `word_id` = 143658; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8500
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $C. At this rate, the Syndicate pest will be rid from the land in no time.' WHERE `word_id` = 132489; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=549
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $C. Now you know the way to get down to Crystalsong Forest and also how to return.' WHERE `word_id` = 161232; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12790
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N - I value a "can do" attitude in those who I work with.$B$BI\'ve been tasked by General Feathermoon to address the naga in a direct manner. My plans are two fold: one, we will weaken their forces both in number and in command, and two, we will uncover what they are up to in the ruins. With your help, we\'ll counter the naga presence without sacrificing the general security of the stronghold.' WHERE `word_id` = 137925; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3130
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N!  Defeating those Dukes will leave the Twilight\'s Hammer reeling for a while. As promised, here\'s your reward. It\'s some of the better stuff Huum and I have found.' WHERE `word_id` = 143404; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8363
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N! The components are gathered and we are ready.$B$BI trust you will be pleased.' WHERE `word_id` = 139424; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4784
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N! You are quite a fast learner.' WHERE `word_id` = 140930; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=6063
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N! You\'d be surprised how many couriers I meet who forget to do something as simple as bring back the mug. Mugs don\'t grow on trees, or so they tell me!$B$BHere\'s a little something for the effort. Thanks again for your help.' WHERE `word_id` = 137994; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3365
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. I\'ve been trying to attempt these books for a very long time. It is fortunate that we were able to be of mutual assistance.' WHERE `word_id` = 147796; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9637
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. In time, the land will heal. We must not give up.' WHERE `word_id` = 137607; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=2975
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. It will be some time before we can assault the hold proper, but until then, we must teach them to fear the Barrens.' WHERE `word_id` = 174849; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24517
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. It\'s all here. All that remains is to forge the weapon.' WHERE `word_id` = 147974; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9692
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. Now, we have most of what we\'ll need to attempt to break Kael\'thas\'s magic.$B$BAnd if the blood elves suffer from the loss of their local commander, so much the better.' WHERE `word_id` = 150518; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10301
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. Thank you.$B$BMagatha told me that if you were successful in finding her clansman that you be given this. Please, take it in thanks.' WHERE `word_id` = 140646; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5724
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. That should put a stop to the attacks once we finish these elementals off.' WHERE `word_id` = 177890; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25574
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. These will do nicely. I will prepare them now while you move on to your last two components. Are you ready?' WHERE `word_id` = 139420; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4783
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. This will be a great weapon against the enemy forces.' WHERE `word_id` = 177565; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25472
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. We will make our way out of here soon enough.' WHERE `word_id` = 186906; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28105
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. With one more healthy guard out there to help the town, we\'ll be that much safer. I\'m glad to see you\'re already learning to use your abilities wisely. If you feel you are ready for more training at any time, please come back to me. But for now, take this robe. It will let others know that you are one of our order. If you don\'t want to wear it, that\'s fine. Later there will be more tests and this robe isn\'t necessary for those.' WHERE `word_id` = 140531; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5624
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. You will see that I\'m true to my word.' WHERE `word_id` = 153476; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11056
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. You\'ve saved me a lot of work!$B$BBut don\'t think that I\'m not grateful!' WHERE `word_id` = 271629; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=6571
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N. Your determination has been duly noted.' WHERE `word_id` = 140838; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5981
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, $N.$B$BI hope this will aid you in your efforts here.' WHERE `word_id` = 154566; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11546
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, a new recruit answering the call to arms against the silithid. Welcome to Cenarion Hold, $C. I am pleased to see the words of our emissaries are reaching heroes of your caliber. You will find no shortage of opportunities to help us in our efforts here and I expect you\'ll quickly prove to be a valuable ally to our cause.' WHERE `word_id` = 143156; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8275
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, Anduin will learn a lot by shadowing you. Remember, stay within the city\'s borders. Keep him out of trouble. And above all else, guard him with your life. Anduin, no adventures! Stay close to $N and return to the keep should you see any trouble.' WHERE `word_id` = 182943; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26960
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, excellent specimens indeed.$B$BThe quilboar are further along than I had expected.$B$BHere, $C, take this and get out of my way. I\'d better take a closer look at these weapons. We may have underestimated our enemy, and that\'s the kind of mistake we can\'t afford to make.' WHERE `word_id` = 133909; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=893
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, excellent!  These are going to work out incredibly well - I can already tell that they\'re going to be much harder when properly cured.$B$BThanks again for your help $N. Here - please take one of my latest creations.' WHERE `word_id` = 142431; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25450
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, excellent, thank you! I may need more of a sample to get truly conclusive results, but you\'ve done well today.' WHERE `word_id` = 163900; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13479
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, it appears everything is here. Now, all I have to do is mix everything together and give it a try. If this tonic does what my research indicates it should do, I may have discovered a way to lessen the effects of my people\'s magic addiction.$B$BYou\'re about to witness history in the making, $N. Just think, without your help, this wouldn\'t have been possible.' WHERE `word_id` = 276146; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9434
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, mon. Now we be talkin\'.' WHERE `word_id` = 143485; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8410
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, mon. That\'s a good start to collecting the sigils we\'ll need to remove Trol\'kalar from Trollbane\'s tomb.' WHERE `word_id` = 132874; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=639
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, more fine tusk specimens, though some look a bit dingy.You have the far-reaching gratitude of the Consortium, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 148920; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9915
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, the power source is yours. Now, it isn\'t completely designed for use in a science kit like that, so you\'ll only have a limited amount of time before all the data you collect will go kablooey!$B$BWhen you collect everything you need for whatever it is you are doing, bring it to me and I\'ll shut it down properly. You\'ll have at most two hours to get what you need to get done, done.$B$BIf you don\'t get it done in time, I can always sell you another power source to try again. You heard me - sell!' WHERE `word_id` = 131755; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=379
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, these should do the trick. And now, if you\'ll permit me, in case anyone\'s listening... THANKS FOR DIGGING ALL OF THESE BONES OUT OF THE GROUND FOR US AND NOT HURTING THE NATIVE BEASTS IN ANY WAY. Whether you really did or didn\'t, I don\'t want to know. Let\'s keep it that way, shall we?  Here - maybe this will keep your lips shut on the whole thing. Anything to get out of here alive, I say!' WHERE `word_id` = 175380; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24730
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, these should do the trick. And now, if you\'ll permit me...$B$BTHANKS FOR DIGGING ALL OF THESE BONES OUT OF THE GROUND FOR US AND NOT HURTING THE NATIVE BEASTS IN ANY WAY.$B$BWhether you really did or didn\'t, I don\'t want to know. Let\'s keep it that way, shall we?  Here - maybe this will keep your lips shut on the whole thing. Anything to get out of here alive, I say!' WHERE `word_id` = 138555; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3882
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent, this completes my report.$B$BI\'ll be sure to mention your kindness to the council, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 161003; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12728
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. As their scouts fail to report in, Talrendis will feel the terror they\'ve tried in vain to inflict on us.' WHERE `word_id` = 173313; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14117
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Did you happen to locate this Lantresor creature that the stupid one\'s letter mentioned?$B$BRegardless, we must press on. I have gotten reports of more ogre activity that must be dealt with at once!' WHERE `word_id` = 148948; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9921
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Here\'s your cut. Good doing business with you.' WHERE `word_id` = 174522; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14486
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. I shall transmute these into something more suitable to our needs.' WHERE `word_id` = 144627; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8947
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. I will cast an augmentation enchantment on the samples so I can more clearly analyze the taint on the soil.' WHERE `word_id` = 146058; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8487
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. I will signal our ground troops to make their move.' WHERE `word_id` = 155335; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11232
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. I\'ll do my best to alter these documents.' WHERE `word_id` = 176960; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25274
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. I\'ll have their bodies strung up along the gold road as a message to the Alliance.' WHERE `word_id` = 174983; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24572
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. I\'ll start rounding up some help to get these cannons positioned.' WHERE `word_id` = 173516; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14204
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. It appears everything is here.$B$BDon\'t worry. your next task will include plenty of opportunities to wield your weapon again, I promise.$B$BI\'ll have an initiate bring it all to Magister Astalor. There\'s no need to send you on such a trivial errand when there are more important things to be done.' WHERE `word_id` = 148114; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9723
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. It\'s important to stay ahead of the enemy\'s next move. This information will allow us to anticipate the Twilight\'s Hammer\'s attacks.' WHERE `word_id` = 143649; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8498
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Just as I suspected all along. I shall have to attempt to contact Ysera and see if she approves.$B$BIf she can be coaxed from her nightmare, of course.$B$BThank you, $N. You have been indispensable.' WHERE `word_id` = 159766; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12459
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Keep bringing me more plant parts if you find any.$B$B<This quest is repeatable up to Honored reputation.>' WHERE `word_id` = 148354; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9784
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Let\'s give it a shot.' WHERE `word_id` = 152213; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10757
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Let\'s see if we can find anything of importance.' WHERE `word_id` = 188360; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28498
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Now that that\'s out of the way...' WHERE `word_id` = 178318; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25684
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Now we can start pushing our ground forces up towards Grim Batol.' WHERE `word_id` = 186848; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28091
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Once I have everything I need I will mix it all together and unleash the voodoo! Woe unto our enemies!' WHERE `word_id` = 179735; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26060
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. That should slow down their assault.' WHERE `word_id` = 162965; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13186
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The converted sentries will help to secure our perimeter.' WHERE `word_id` = 154489; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11525
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The defenses should hold off the Scourge a bit longer. Thank you for lending us a hand, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 146071; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8490
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The dogs will be well fed and ready to defend our outpost for weeks!' WHERE `word_id` = 179333; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25935
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The formulae etched into this tablet will consume days of research, but I am confident such research will bear sweet fruit.$B$BThank you, $N. You have been invaluable to us.' WHERE `word_id` = 139395; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4768
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The less interference from the Alliance, the better.' WHERE `word_id` = 176032; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25019
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The march of the Forsaken continues.' WHERE `word_id` = 179718; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26053
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. The spirits of the raptors that gave these eyes will lend strength to the bearer of this amulet.' WHERE `word_id` = 133016; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=672
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. These combined with the skin will make for a flawless clone of the constructs the iron dwarves use.' WHERE `word_id` = 156734; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11483
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. These look to be usable samples.$B$BTime again to use the enemy\'s strength against them....' WHERE `word_id` = 163341; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13277
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. This is just what we needed. It\'s going to be a chore keeping all the tables stocked with fresh food, but it\'s well worth it.' WHERE `word_id` = 164595; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14023
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. This little pup will grow to be strong and merciless like his father.' WHERE `word_id` = 177007; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25294
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. This will allow me to finish my last task and hopefully gain the form of the wolf!' WHERE `word_id` = 179328; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25934
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. This will keep us in business while we wait for the Sha\'tar to finish whatever housekeeping it is they need to do inside Oshu\'gun.' WHERE `word_id` = 148823; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9893
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Valus must have received my report.$B$BLet\'s get to work, $R.' WHERE `word_id` = 161228; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12789
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. We could surely devise some incredibly powerful armor from this chitin. Here\'s the riches you were promised.' WHERE `word_id` = 144431; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8858
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. We were in need of these, $N. Good work.' WHERE `word_id` = 272043; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8540
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. When combined with the mojo, these fluids will dilute the effectiveness of the mojo without completely eliminating it.$B$BNow, one more thing.' WHERE `word_id` = 159985; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12510
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. When they begin to flee in fear, the ward shall be there to wish them a fond farewell.' WHERE `word_id` = 159243; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12261
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. When we make our move against Abyssion, we should be able to do so without reinforcements coming to his aid.' WHERE `word_id` = 182586; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26861
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. With these fragments, we can calibrate a bomb that will destroy the void conduit atop Ultris. With the void conduit destroyed, Dimensius\'s connection with the void will be severed and he will be left defenseless!' WHERE `word_id` = 151052; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10437
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. You\'ll see, this can\'t possibly go wrong!' WHERE `word_id` = 186250; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27924
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent. Your success shows that you are prepared.$B$BOf all the elements, earth represents the foundation of all things. It is your strength, your stamina, and your patience. Earth will protect you, but only if shown the proper respect. Like the other elements, even earth can be fickle. Earth is the basis for life, and by observing its laws, you will gain greater wisdom. Never forget the secrets earth shares with you.$B$BI shall make a sapta for you now, and by accepting it, you will realize your path.' WHERE `word_id` = 135877; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1516
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent.$B$B<You heard a series of clicking sounds.>$B$BNow to vanquish our other foe.' WHERE `word_id` = 191408; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29826
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent... each bijou we wrest away from the Blood God\'s minions is one step closer we all are to finally defeating them once and for all. You bring honor to the Zandalar - and yourself - through your noble actions.$B$BRemember $N, you may always destroy the bijous you find in Zul\'Gurub at the altar. For each one, you will gain recognition and an Honor Token!  Just remember to have an open space in your inventory if you don\'t have one of the tokens already.' WHERE `word_id` = 143085; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8240
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellent... I was never able to gain access to this text, it was held in a protected wing of the library that would have looked suspicious for me to be loitering around.$B$BWell, you did a good job in getting this, and I\'m convinced that you can probably handle your own imp, so there\'s no reason for me not to show you how to summon one.' WHERE `word_id` = 135980; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1598
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellently done, $N. And now, with the leader of the Scourge forces eliminated from Andorhal, we bide our time.' WHERE `word_id` = 182793; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26924
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellently done, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 183553; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27117
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excellently done. You have served the Dark Lady well today, $N. This virulent blood will supply our armies with all manner of powerful weapons against the disgusting Alliance. We will wipe them from these lands. For the Horde, of course... and all thanks to you.' WHERE `word_id` = 181069; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26419
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Excuse me for my cold reception, $N, but as I\'m sure you can tell, I am an extremely busy man. I see that you have impressed Calor--and I assure you, that is no small feat--and that he has given his recommendation.$B$BThere are unsavory types afoot, $N, and we can use the help of all who have proven themselves. We battle against demons, the undead, and those who would provide them aid. Be vigilant, be wary, and trust none who would not give aid to our cause.$B$BGlory under the Light.' WHERE `word_id` = 131093; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=223
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Executed with quickness and discretion. A job well done.' WHERE `word_id` = 176597; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25172
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Executor Zygand asked me to take stock of our equipment here in Brill. With the Scourge, and worse, lurking in the woods, he doesn\'t want the Deathguards to lack gear they might need.$B$BI found that we are, in general, well stocked, but we do need more weapons to replace those lost in the field.$B$BHere is a requisition order of what is needed, for the weapon dealer Gordon Wendham in the Undercity. Take the order to Bat Handler Anette and speak with her about transport to the Undercity.' WHERE `word_id` = 167991; -- locales_quest - details : entry=6321
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Exellent $N !$B , you got everything just as i asked and now i can make a Cryptstalker Boots.' WHERE `word_id` = 144916; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9058
