UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Falla sent you to me? Well now, let\'s see that shard that you say she was so hesitant to talk about...$B$B<Hamuul peers into the shard>$B$BOh... I didn\'t... Well.$B$B$N, thank you for delivering this to me. It isn\'t wise to speak of things such as this, though, I advise you. These are matters that you should not concern yourself with.$B$BLet\'s just say that things in the Emerald Dream are not as we thought...$B$BPerhaps in the future, our paths may cross again.' WHERE `word_id` = 138009; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3369
