UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For a $R who has spent so much time inside Gnomeregan, you look positively fit and healthy, $N. That\'s good. Before we can complete what Operation: Gnomeregan began, we\'re going to need more warriors like you.' WHERE `word_id` = 180244; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26203
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For a moment there, I thought all was lost. Even when surrounded by the worgen in Gilneas I had higher hopes! But you proved me wrong $N. I will see to it that Sylvanas herself hears of your triumph here today. Don\'t worry about the mess here, I will gladly see to it myself.' WHERE `word_id` = 186548; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27998
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For a small fee you can buy a gryphon ride to Kharanos... as long as you\'ve already been there. Gryphons will only fly you to places you\'ve already been, so be sure to speak with every gryphon master you see so you can fly to him later.$B$BYou\'ve already been to Brolan, the gryphon master of Kharanos, so now you can return to him. And once in Kharanos, you can deliver the picks to Gremlock Pilsnor.$B$BSpeak with me when you\'re ready to go.' WHERE `word_id` = 168055; -- locales_quest - details : entry=6392
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For a thousand years, all we have known is conflict. We have defended our people from the attacks of both void creature and ethereal alike.$B$BNow, one of our most hated enemies lies dead - finally.$B$BI give you the thanks of a hundred million ethereals, fleshling.' WHERE `word_id` = 151062; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10439
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For centuries, we lived in relative peace with the creatures of the land. Several months ago, Kurz began to see dark omens. The peace that we enjoyed for so long was to be lost. The extent of the catastrophe could not be known!$B$BSo it would be that the gods would shatter our land - turning both friend and foe against us. But there was something else... Amidst the chaos, a hero would rise: A hero not of Stillpine blood. The Promised One would deliver us from devastation.$B$BThat prophesied hero was you.' WHERE `word_id` = 147474; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9559
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For countless ages I have walked these forests and lived in these mountains. Through snow and fire, I have watched civilizations crumble and nature press on. Now, the very earth turns against us, and it becomes very apparent that we must fight if our legacy is to continue. Your heart is true, and I would choose you as our champion. If you value the thick hide and resilience of my kind, then accept my boon. Know that the other spirits will not accept you once this choice is made, so choose wisely.' WHERE `word_id` = 172296; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13597
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For decades has the garrison at Nethergarde held firm against the threat of the Horde and we do not intend to surrender now.' WHERE `word_id` = 188968; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28673
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For every val\'kyr you slay, you save dozens of our men... and prevent the Forsaken forces from growing. Still, they press on. We may not win this battle after all.' WHERE `word_id` = 183818; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27201
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For generations to come, they will sing songs of this day, $N - songs of your valor. I wish Thrall had been here to celebrate this victory with us. The Legion is undone - and Hellfire now belongs to the Horde once again! There may yet be hope for this ravaged world - and our peoples\' place within it. $B$BLok\'tar ogar!' WHERE `word_id` = 149796; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10136
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For generations, the forces of Strom and Arathor ravaged the trolls. Now their greatest weapon is in our hands. Our inching progress in the steamy forests of Zul\'Gurub will be no more.$B$BYour assistance has been great, $N, and the Darkspear trolls are indebted to you.$B$BI will be sure that the sword is delivered to Nimboya at Grom\'gol.' WHERE `word_id` = 132905; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=646
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For many long years I have concentrated my efforts on perfecting the ways of communicating with nature. This is but a small part of the untapped potential that beasts can bring to you.' WHERE `word_id` = 152110; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10720
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For me? You\'re a true hero, $N!' WHERE `word_id` = 131444; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=308
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For my gratitude, this is for you, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 139487; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4841
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For so many years I was held under her captivating gaze. Finally, to see justice meted and the honor of Stormwind restored! Today, we celebrate this glorious victory!' WHERE `word_id` = 142124; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=7495
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For some reason they all think that you\'ve been sent by Magatha Grimtotem. I know it must have something to do with that wind serpent that\'s been hanging around. Doesn\'t matter. Their leader is dead. It\'s only a matter of time before the tauren of Freewind Post regain their home. If I were them, I\'d push back a little to teach the Grimtotem a lesson, but they probably won\'t. They\'re tauren.' WHERE `word_id` = 184111; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27327
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For ten thousand years I drifted without form within the Emerald Dream. I awake to a nightmare.$B$B$R, seek out the dreamer - the dragon aspect you call Ysera - and let her know that I have returned and will aid the Guardians of Hyjal as they crush the Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BI will fill their skies with suffering.' WHERE `word_id` = 178881; -- locales_quest - details : entry=25833
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For the Alliance! You\'re a strong one, $N. Strong enough to crack some vrykul skull at Nifflevar.' WHERE `word_id` = 335645; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11429
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For the time being. I shall give you what you need to focus your spells and to call upon the spirits of air. Take this totem, and when you are ready, train with me some more.' WHERE `word_id` = 135928; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1531
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For too long have the Horde been left unchecked. We allowed their territories to prosper and in return for our generosity they plotted and planned our demise.$B$BPeace? Useless... It\'s gotten us nowhere. We have lost some of our greatest heroes to "peace." Let us see what battle brings...$B$BReturn to Northrend, $N. Conquer it for your king - FOR THE ALLIANCE!' WHERE `word_id` = 163723; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13377
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='For your toubles you may choose your reward.' WHERE `word_id` = 145908; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8325
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Force Commander Danath may have misunderstood my request for reinforcements. You look capable, but... I asked for a full sized battalion!$B$BYou see, we have a bit of a demon problem...' WHERE `word_id` = 149816; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10141
