UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Kosak sent you, eh? Surprising. I thought for sure that he\'d be dead by now. Well if you made it past the blockade then you definitely have something that we can use. Now, do you have any news of the Horde? What are they doing? Where are they going? Tell me everything.' WHERE `word_id` = 178678; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25765
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Kovic slain??! This is a glorious day, $N! For years that scoundrel has been running shady undermarket trades, undercutting honest, hard working traders all over the world.$B$BYou deserve a fine reward for this accomplishment! And a fine reward you shall have!' WHERE `word_id` = 138072; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3402
