UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Quel\'Delar rises again, as the sin\'dorei have risen from the ashes of defeat and betrayal. Yet, somehow, the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker has chosen to serve an outsider.$B$BBe at ease, $N. I do not mean to diminish your accomplishment, for you have done what none of my brothers could, although I do not know why. You are clearly meant to be its bearer; the blade is already adapting itself to your abilities. Wield Quel\'Delar proudly against our common foes.' WHERE `word_id` = 165179; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24801
