UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Samuelson - corrupted by the Twilight\'s Hammer? This must have been going on for years. Right here in my very keep! I am grateful that you and my son were able to get to the bottom of this before my city was brought to harm. I\'ve underestimated how much Anduin has grown - his command of the holy light just saved my life, if not the entire kingdom. As for you - words alone can\'t do justice to your heroism this day. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `word_id` = 183519; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27106
